  "original_title": "\u0db8\u0dc4\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbb,\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0d91\u0dc5\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d87\u0dad\u0dd4\u0db5 \u0db4\u0dc5\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd3\u0db4\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rains in several provinces including Kandy, Nuwara Eliya",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, there will be several periods of rain in Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-Western provinces and in Kandy, Nuwara Eliya, Galle and Matara districts today (19).",
        "A spokesman for the department said that rain or thundershowers will occur in places in Uva, Eastern and North Central Provinces and Mullaitivu District in the evening or at night.",
        "He mentioned that in the southern province, there are 40, 50 km/h fast winds from time to time.",
        "The department also states that thunderstorms may be accompanied by lightning and temporary gusty winds."
      ],
